title: Tammy's Corner House Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A laid back local cafe on a main street running through Hermosa Beach. Offers weekend brunch. Large menu includes smoothies, scrambles, burritos (can substitute meat sausage with veggie sausage and omit cheese), pancakes (there's a flour-less flax meal), french toast, bagel sandwiches, both sweet and savory crepes, oatmeal topped with fresh fruit, soy and almond milk.
